15 following sections:
16 (a) 7-3-301;
17 (b) 7-3-303;
18 (c) 7-3-304;
19 (d) 7-3-305;
20 (e) 7-3-312(2);
21 (f) 7-3-313(1) or (2);
22 (g) 7-3-314(2) 7-3-314;
23 (h) 7-3-315(1);
24 (i) 7-3-316(2);
25 (j) 7-3-317(2);
26 (k) 7-3-318.
